'''Group Fair''' is a coordinated community [[Special:MyLanguage/Events|event]], partnered with [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]]. The Group Fair event helps users explore different [[Special:MyLanguage/Groups|Groups]] and communities within the platform. The event is scheduled from October 24, 2025 to October 26, 2025<ref>[https://x.com/VRChat/status/1981571353372500120 "Groups Fair is live on Open Beta this weekend! (Oct 24–26)"], posted by ''[https://x.com/VRChat VRChat on X.com]''. Dated October 24, 2025. Retrieved October 24, 2025.</ref><ref>[https://bsky.app/profile/vrchat.com/post/3m3x5vzsqzc2u "Visit the Group Fair this weekend on Open Beta!"], posted by ''[https://bsky.app/profile/vrchat.com VRChat on Bluesky]''. Dated October 24, 2025. Retrieved October 24, 2025.</ref>.

==Overview==
[[File:GroupFairIPS.webp|thumb|VRChat's IPS banner to promote the Groups Fair, on the Launch Pad.]]
Groups Fair makes use of the "Live Now" tab on the 2024.4.1 [[Open Beta]], as well as the [[Calendar]] on the [[Quick Menu]].

